  <summary date="2022-11-03T13:52:40Z" status="Introduced in House">Chase COVID Unemployment Fraud Act of 2022

This bill addresses fraud and overpayments of pandemic unemployment assistance, including by allowing states to retain a specified percentage of recovered funds and prohibiting the Department of Labor from allowing blanket waivers of overpayments.</summary>
